cd2.cd_education_status      and      ws_sales_price between 150.00 and 200.00     )    )    and    (     (      ca_country = 'United States'      and      ca_state in ('KY', 'NC', 'SD')      and ws_net_profit between 100 and 200     )     or     (      ca_country = 'United States'      and      ca_state in ('AR', 'GA', 'IN')      and ws_net_profit between 150 and 300     )     or     (      ca_country = 'United States'      and      ca_state in ('KS', 'OH', 'VA')      and ws_net_profit between 50 and 250     )    ) group by r_reason_desc order by substring(r_reason_desc,1,20)         ,avg(ws_quantity)         ,avg(wr_refunded_cash)         ,avg(wr_fee) limit 100
